    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Radfordia (M.) hylandi Fain and Lukoschus, 1977 from Microtus pennsylvanicus, female. A, dorsal view; B, ventral view; C, seta m, D, vulvar region. Scale bars: A, B = 100 µm; C, D = 50 µm." ;
