<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5282123>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. Radfordia (M.) hylandi Fain and Lukoschus, 1977, male from Microtus pennsylvanicus. A, dorsal view; B, ventral view; C, seta m; D, genital cone. Specimen from fossil Microtus miurus. E, genital cone. Scale bars: A, B = 100 µm; C–E = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5282123/files/figure.png" ;
